OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be cloudy
OL,6,Fwith some patchy rain. This afternoon
OL,7,Fwill become dry with the chance of
OL,8,Fsome bright spells across Edinburgh,
OL,9,FLothian and eastern Borders. Becoming
OL,10,Fvery mild in any sunshine in the east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,13,Fclear periods. Then the rest of the
OL,14,Fnight will remain dry with variable
OL,15,Famounts of cloud. Strong southerly
OL,16,Fwinds developing along the Solway
OL,17,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
