OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FThe morning will be dry,
OL,6,Fsome hazy sunshine in the east. Rain
OL,7,Fwill gradually spread east across all
OL,8,Fparts through the afternoon and
OL,9,Fevening. Mild across the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA cold
OL,12,Fstart with some frost on Friday, then
OL,13,Fa dry and sunny day, Dry and bright on
OL,14,FSaturday, clouding over later. Cloudy
OL,15,Fwith a chance of rain on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
